    "Condition : 1 - The development shall be carried out in accordance with the reports, specifications and drawings detailed Sheet 3 (Furniture Arrangement Plan), Sheet 5 (Proposed Elevation), Sheet 7 (Proposed Section), Sheet 8 (Proposed Signage Detail), Sheet 9 (Street View), Sheet 10 (Rendering). \r\nReason: To ensure a satisfactory standard of development and to allow the local planning authority to review any potential changes to the scheme. \r\n",
